OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FIsraeli troops killed a seven-month-
OL,8,Fold Palestinian baby boy after firing
OL,9,Fat his parents' vehicle in the
OL,10,Foccupied West Bank, the Palestinian
OL,11,Fhealth ministry has said.
OL,13,FSam Fahd Abu Haikal was killed Friday
OL,14,Fevening, and his parents were wounded
OL,15,Fwhile driving in the Tel Rumeida area
OL,16,Fsouth of Hebron City, according to the
OL,17,Fministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
