PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FThe official Palestinian news agency
OL,8,FWAFA said the baby was critically
OL,9,Fwounded after being struck in the face
OL,10,Fby the same bullet that injured his
OL,11,Fmother. He later died of his injuries.
OL,12,FHis father, Fahd Abu Haikal, a
OL,13,Flecturer at Bethlehem University, was
OL,14,Fshot in the hand. They were travelling
OL,15,Ffrom Bethlehem to visit family in
OL,16,FHebron when soldiers opened fire, the
OL,17,Fagency reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
