PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FIsrael's military has scaled up
OL,8,Fmilitary operations in the West Bank
OL,9,Fsince the terrorist attack by Hamas on
OL,10,FOctober 7, 2023, that killed some
OL,11,F1,200 people and took 251 people
OL,12,Fhostage, triggering the war in Gaza.
OL,14,FIsrael's retaliatory military campaign
OL,15,Fhas so far killed more than 72,900
OL,16,FPalestinians, according to Gaza's
OL,17,FHealth Ministry. The ministry, which
OL,18,Fis part of the Hamas-led government,
OL,19,Fis generally seen as reliable by
OL,20,FUnited Nations agencies and
OL,21,Findependent experts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FThe United Nations said last month
OL,8,Fthat more than 1,000 Palestinians have
OL,9,Fbeen killed in the West Bank and east
OL,10,FJerusalem since the war began, at
OL,11,Fleast 240 of them children. 49 people
OL,12,Fhave been killed since the start of
OL,13,Fthis year, it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
