PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FThe Israeli military said on Friday
OL,8,Fthat an initial inquiry found that the
OL,9,Finjured were uninvolved civilians and
OL,10,Fsaid the situation is under review. It
OL,11,Falso said soldiers shot at a vehicle
OL,12,Fthat was perceived to be accelerating
OL,13,Ftoward them in the Hebron area. It
OL,14,Fsaid soldiers responded with single
OL,15,Fshots, wounding three Palestinians who
OL,16,Fwere evacuated for medical treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
