PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FAt Al-Ahly Hospital in Hebron, the
OL,8,Fbaby's father told Associated Press
OL,9,Freporters that a bullet struck the
OL,10,Fcar's windshield before piercing his
OL,11,Fhand, then his son and wife.
OL,13,F"It entered the child's face on the
OL,14,Fright side and exited on the left,
OL,15,Fthen passed directly into his mother's
OL,16,Fface and exited on the other side,
OL,17,Fwith shrapnel lodged near her heart,"
OL,18,FAbu Haikal said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
