OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FThe mother is in critical condition
OL,8,Fbecause there's shrapnel close to her
OL,9,Fheart, he said. They haven't told her
OL,10,Fyet that her son, who turned seven
OL,11,Fmonths old on Friday, was killed.
OL,13,FThe baby's grandmother, Feryal Abu
OL,14,FHeikal, was in the car during the
OL,15,Fshooting and said they were driving
OL,16,Fnear a checkpoint and stopped when
OL,17,Fthey saw Israeli military vehicles and
OL,18,Fsoldiers in the distance. As the
OL,19,Fforces fired at them, she initially
OL,20,Fthought it was warning shots before
OL,21,Fthey were struck, she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780876973
OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,F"The scene was horrific to see a seven-
OL,8,Fmonth-old baby with a smashed face,"
OL,9,Fshe said. "What kind of army in the
OL,10,Fworld does this? ... What happened to
OL,11,Fmy grandson can't be easily forgotten."
OL,13,FThe baby's funeral is expected later
OL,14,FSaturday.
