OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FIn March, Israeli soldiers fired on a
OL,8,Fcar carrying a family in the northern
OL,9,FWest Bank, killing four people,
OL,10,Fincluding two children, the
OL,11,FPalestinian Authority's Health
OL,12,FMinistry said at the time.
OL,14,FIsraeli soldiers accused of harming
OL,15,FPalestinians are rarely penalised and
OL,16,Fwere indicted in fewer than 1% of
OL,17,Fcases based on 2,427 complaints
OL,18,Falleging wrongdoing between 2016 and
OL,19,F2024, according to Israeli rights
OL,20,Fgroup Yesh Din.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
