OL,3,CIsraeli forces kill a Palestinian baby
OL,4,Cin the occupied West Bank, say
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FMore than 700,000 Israelis live in the
OL,8,Foccupied West Bank and east Jerusalem,
OL,9,Fterritories captured by Israel in 1967
OL,10,Ffrom Jordan and sought by the
OL,11,FPalestinians for a future state.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
